---
title: Fundamental Learner’s Imperatives
category: concept
status: draft
---

1. Show me where I am
2. Show me what I can achieve
3. Explain me what to do
4. Let me take my pace
5. Support me keep my pace
6. Help me when I am stuck
7. Let me continue from where I left off
8. Let me repeat when I need
9. Let me focus on my way
10. Let me decide
